    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, we've got a situation. A small group of users' emails were exposed because of an S3 bucket misconfiguration that's been sitting open for a few days. It's only 50 people, but if this hits the press as a \"security lapse\" or \"human error,\" our brand sentiment scores are going to tank. I need a way to frame this to the media that doesn't make us look incompetent. How do we pitch this?",
